{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124780/extras/SteamGifRats.gif?t=1733178037\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Purrfect Alchemy</i></strong> is a <strong>4 Player</strong>, <strong>Wizard Cat</strong> themed, <strong>Wave Survival</strong>, <strong>Tower Defense</strong> game!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Play as a wizard cat from 1 of 4 classes: Earth, Air, Ice and Fire. Travel through the depths of caves and far reaches of dangerous fields as you and your furry companions defeat creatures of evil. Spitting snakes, thieving rats, rolling beetles and explosive puffers!?! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As these enemies stand in your way of adventure, you must harness the power of <i>Alchemy</i> to survive. Use <i>crafting cards</i> and gather ingredients to create your defenses. Create anything from, arrow flinging turrets to player healing pylons. Progress through each level through tremendous tasks. Defeat bosses, upgrade spells and meddle with merchants as you and your friends reach the end of your journey in\u00a0<i><strong>Purrfect Alchemy.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Local multiplayer is only possible by connecting controllers.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3124780/extras/SteamGif2.gif?t=1733178037\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Craft &amp; Brew</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create <i>defenses</i> and <i>towers</i> to help you on your journey and through tougher waves of enemies. Use ingredients you find, or purchase from the merchant. See what secrets you can craft using the power of Alchemy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" sr